\mt1 Taetas  
\imt1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ô rani m…ô n…ôfe i n…ôkuku…ô  
\ip Taetas in riti n…ôha Pol. Iasitu riti s…ôv…ôi Pol. N…ôp…®n nepw…®n in ramav…ôn irau Pol. Nakalasia me fwe t…ôn…ô …ômwer…®s riti kani m…ô Krit, Taetas in i…ôm…ô asori riti s…ôv…ônraha. N…ôkuku…ô i r…ômwhen ia n…ôkuku…ô mi s…ôv…ôi Timoti. Nakalasia me fwe Krit h…ôpkukur…ôn amasan mh…ô noien s…ôv…ôi n…ôfwakiien t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô ir…ôha h…ôpkuvehe vi a mhahat…ôt…ô ia Kristo. Ro pen i…ôrmama tram…ôkeikei mev…ôn masitu ia nir…ôha. Pol r…®ni pen t…® Taetas m…®ne nakalasia me fwe ik…®n m…ô tuh…ôfar…ô ir…ô. Pol r…®ni pen t…® Taetas m…ô trahat…ôn ir…ôha ia n…®p…ôrhienien. In rahat…ôn mwi Taetas ia niriien nakalasia me.  
\c 1  
\s1 Pol ramrai n…ôkuku…ô i m Taetas  
\p
\v 1 Iou Pol, iou i…ôrmama riti s…ô iakamo tukwini nari m Kumwes…ôn, n…ôn…ô iou aposol riti s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo. In r…ôrhi pen iou m…ô takasitu ia n…ôrmama me s…ôm…ôme Kumwes…ôn ruv…ôrfi raka ir…ôha. In rokeikei m…ô takasitu ia nir…ôha ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôv…ônraha, n…ôn…ô masitu mwi ia nir…ôha m…ô tuh…ôukur…ôn n…ô…°kiariien p…ôrhien s…ô ramahat…ôn noien me Kumwes…ôn rokeikei.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Kol 1:27\x*In r…ôrhi pen iou m…ô takasitu ia nir…ôha pw…ôh h…ômri pen …ôknek…®n n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônraha ia n…®m…®ruien rer…®n. Fwe tui, n…ôp…®n t…®pr…ôn…ô ramiw…ôn ihi, Kumwes…ôn s…ô r…®pkeiku…ô mh…ô ruv…ôni raka m…ô truvei pen n…®m…®ruien rer…®n n…ôha m…®nraha,  
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Efes 1:9-10, Taet 2:10, 3:4, 1Tim 1:1,11\x*n…ôn…ô ia n…ôp…®n atukwatukw s…ôv…ônhi in ro pui n…®m…®ruien n…ôha ia n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ônhi. Kumwes…ôn s…ô rauvehim…®ru k…®taha r…ômri pehe n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha ia r…ô…°…®k m…®ni n…ôkwan m…ô tak…ôvisau irapw ir…ô.   
\p
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt 2Kor 8:23, Kal 2:3, 2Tim 1:2, 4:10, Rom 1:7\x*N…ôkuku…ô i rauvehe tukw ik Taetas. Ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôkrau ik…ômwhen ia n…ôr…®k p…ôrhien. Pw…ôh Kumwes…ôn Tata s…ôk…®taha m…®ne Iesu Kristo s…ô rauvehim…®ru k…®taha trou…ôriari pehe namasanien m…®ne n…ôm…ôrinuien mik.   
\s1 Wok s…ô Taetas ramo ia t…ôn…ô Krit  
\p
\v 5 Iak…®n…ôpw…ôh ik ia t…ôn…ô Krit m…ô tik…ômri atukwatukw narimnari me s…ôm…ôme krau kr…®pko mh…ô sampam ir…ô. R…ômwhen iak…®m…ôni pehe tukw ik i, tikam…ôkeikei mev…ôn ia rukw…ônu me pam muvehi ut…ô elta me s…ôv…ôi n…ôfwakiien.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt 1Tim 3:2-7, 2Tim 2:24-26\x*Ikukur…ôn nuvehi ut…ôien i…ôrmama riti tr…®ni m…®nu…ô noien s…ôv…ônhi ratukwatukw pam, s…ôv…ônhi pran kuatia, n…®pwn…ôt…®n me kamh…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ia Iesu, k…®pk…®ni mh…ô ir…ôha m…ô k…ônkapw…ônraha r…®skai, u…ô h…ôpw…ôh n…®siaiien tata m…®ne mama s…ôv…ônraha.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt 1Kor 4:1\x*I…ôm…ô asori s…ô ram…ôtui t…® nakalasia me ramo tukwini nari m Kumwes…ôn, ro iam…®nhi ir…ô noien s…ôv…ônhi tram…ôkeikei matukwatukw pam. R…ôr…ôha m…ô k…ônkapw…ô r…®skai, u…ô niemaha ram…ôpi akwauakw in, u…ô ram…ôn…®mwi p…®k, u…ô ramousi i…ôrmama, u…ô ramo noien ikou mauvehi mane ir…ô.  
\v 8 M…ôt…ô i…ôrmama s…ô rauvehi wok i tram…ôkeikei mo iam…®nhi ir…ô: In ram…ôsev…ôr ia rukw…ônu s…ôv…ônhi t…® n…ôrmama pw…®spw…®s me. In rokeikei noien amasan, n…ôn…ô mukur…ôn nari. In ramo noien atukwatukw m…®ne noien s…ô r…ômher mo ikinan i. In ramatuak…ôm amasan.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt 2Tim 4:3, Taet 2:1\x*In tram…ôkeikei m…ôkwt…ômhiri …ôknek…®n n…ô…°kiariien p…ôrhien s…ô k…®nahat…ôn in ir…ô. Ia noien n…ôha in rukur…ôn nasituien ia n…ôrmama, mahat…ôn ir…ôha ia n…ô…°kiariien atukwatukw, mukur…ôn mwi n…ômri atukwatukwien n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôni n…ô…°kiariien s…ô rop…ô ia n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha.   
\p
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt 1Tim 4:7\x*Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôrmama h…ôp…®k k…ônkapw…ônraha r…®skai. Ir…ôha kamh…ôni n…ô…°kiariien me nepw…®n n…®pwran riw…ôn, mamheiku…ô ia n…ôrmama. P…ôrhien n…ôkur Isrel me nepw…®n n…ôha ir…ôha kamho iam…®nhi ir…ô mh…ôpi raka n…ôrmama me nepw…®n. Ir…ôha kamh…ôni m…ô tukam…ôkeikei kuvehi ninhum m n…ôrmama t…® nahat…ôn penien m…ô ir…ôha n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Jon 10:12, 1Tes 5:2, 2Tim 3:6\x*Tik…ôr…ôpinh…ô r…ô ia n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ônraha, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô ir…ôha kamhouraha n…ôrmama pam ia n…ôkwai nimw…ô nepw…®n, mamhahat…ôn n…ôrmama ia n…ô…°kiariien s…ô r…®pkatukwatukw mh…ô m…ô tukahat…ôn. Ir…ôha kamho m…ô tuh…ôuvehi mane ir…ô, mh…ôpw…ôh naur…®sien i.  
\v 12 I…ôm…ô Krit riti kupw…ôn in profet riti s…ôv…ônraha, in mwi r…®m…ôni iam…®nhi m…ô, ‚ÄúN…ôkur Krit ir…ôha n…ôrmama s…ôv…ôi neiku…ôien ia n…ôp…®n me pam. Ir…ôha h…ômwhen ia n…ôri …ôprm…®n me. Ir…ôha rarpaha me. N…ôp…®n me ir…ôha hokeikei m…ô tuhamani a nari.‚Äù  
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt 2Tim 4:2\x*N…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi profet n…ôha ro a n…®p…ôrhienien. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô tik…ô…°kiari skai m…®nraha pw…ôh ir…ôha h…ôuvehe mhahat…ôt…ô ia n…ô…°kiariien s…ô ratukwatukw,  
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt 1Tim 4:7\x*mh…ôpw…ôh nesi penien kw…ôna…°ei me s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Isrel m…®ne natuak…ômien me s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama me s…ôm…ôme h…ôn…ôpw…ôh n…ô…°kiariien p…ôrhien.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15 \xt Mat 15:11, Rom 14:20\x*N…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme h…ômher ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn nari riti riw…ôn s…ô tro ir…ôha h…ôuvehe mh…ômkem…®k. M…ôt…ô n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme h…ômkem…®k ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô h…ôpw…ôh n…®niien n…®p…ôrhienien ia Iesu, n…ôn…ô noien riti riw…ôn s…ô tro ir…ôha h…ômher. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônraha ramev…ôn …ôpa t…® n…ôr…ôhaien, h…ôreirei n…ôkiriien noien me.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt 2Tim 3:5, 1Jon 1:6, 2:4\x*Ir…ôha h…ôni m…ô h…ôukur…ôn Kumwes…ôn, m…ôt…ô noien s…ôv…ônraha ramahat…ôn pen m…ô rek…ôm ir…ôha h…ôreirei in. N…ôrmama me n…ôha h…ôr…ôha anan, mamh…ôrui n…ôkwai Kumwes…ôn. Ir…ôha ko h…ôpko mh…ô nari amasan riti.   
\c 2  
\s1 Taetas tram…ôkeikei mahat…ôn n…ô…°kiariien s…ô ratukwatukw  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Taet 1:9\x*M…ôt…ô ik Taetas n…ô…°kiariien s…ôim tram…ôkeikei mesi pen n…ô…°kiariien kamahat…ôn n…ôrmama ir…ô s…ô ratukwatukw.  
\v 2 Tikahat…ôn n…ôr…°har…ô me m…ô r…ôr…ôha ir…ôha n…ôrmama s…ôv…ôi n…ôn…®mwiien. Ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôukur…ôn nari, pw…ôh n…ôrmama h…ôsiai ir…ôha. Ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mamhahat…ôt…ô p…ôrhien, mamhokeikei n…ôrmama, mamh…ôrer …ôknek…®n ia n…ôp…®n me.   
\p
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt 1Tim 3:11\x*Ia noien kuatia a, tikahat…ôn n…®pr…ônem…ô me m…ô ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mho noien s…ô ro ikinan i r…ômwhen s…ô Kumwes…ôn rokeikei. R…ôr…ôha m…ô ir…ôha kamh…ôni n…®kare n…ôrmama, u…ô kamh…ôn…®mwi p…®k n…ôn…®mwien skai r…ômwhen ia waen. Ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mhahat…ôn n…ô…°kiariien s…ô ramasan,  
\v 4 mamh…ôv…ôha…° m n…®pran me s…ôm…ôme har…ô vi a ir…ôha n…ôrman m…ô ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mhokeikei s…ôv…ônraha me n…ôrman me m…®ne n…®pwn…ôt…®nraha me.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Efes 5:22\x*Ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôv…ôha…° m n…®pran me i m…ô ir…ôha tuh…ôuvehe mho ir…ôha n…®pran me s…ôm…ôme h…ôukur…ôn nari, mh…ômher, mamh…ôtui amasan t…® narimnari me fwe ia rukw…ônu, n…ôn…ô mamh…ôsiai n…ôrman me s…ôv…ônraha. N…ôp…®n kamho noien s…ô ro iam…®nhi, n…ôn…ô, tuh…ôr…ôpinh…ô ia n…ôrmama me m…ô tuh…ôpw…ôh n…®ni …ôr…ôhaien n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn.   
\p
\v 6 Ia noien kuatia a mwi, tik…ô…°kiari amasan m nt…ômaru…ô me m…ô ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mho narimnari me s…ô ramahat…ôn pen m…ô ir…ôha h…ôukur…ôn nari.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt 1Tim 4:12, 1Tes 5:3\x*N…ôn…ô ik, ia narimnari me pam, tikamo a noien s…ô ramasan pw…ôh ir…ôha hesi pen n…ôfe ikamo. N…ôp…®n tikahat…ôn, n…®m…®ruien s…ôim tram…ôkeikei matukwatukw mo n…ô…°kiariien s…ôim r…®pam mo n…ôrmama h…ôsiai ir…ô.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt 1Tes 2:15\x*Tikam…ôkeikei mam…®ni a n…ô…°kiariien p…ôrhien m…ô n…ôrmama tuh…ôpw…ôh n…ôtoniien t…ôkutai n…ô…°kiariien s…ôim mh…ôni …ôr…ôha. Pw…ôh in tro n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme ham…ômw…ôki ik tuhaur…®s tukwe t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô ir…ôha h…ôpk…ôtoni mh…ô noien …ôr…ôha riti s…ôim, n…ôn…ô, mh…ôpw…ôh n…®ni …ôr…ôhaien k…®taha.   
\p
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt 1Tim 6:1\x*Tikahat…ôn slef me m…ô ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mho n…ôkwai n…ôm…ô asori me s…ôv…ônraha ia narimnari me pam pw…ôh rer…®nraha ra…°ien t…® wok s…ôv…ônraha. Slef me tuh…ôpw…ôh n…®niien tai n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi n…ôm…ô asori me s…ôv…ônraha,  
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Taet 1:3\x*n…ôn…ô, mh…ôpw…ôh nakresien m…®nraha. M…ôt…ô n…ôp…®n me pam ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mho amasan nari pw…ôh n…ôm…ô asori me s…ôv…ônraha tuh…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ia wok s…ôv…ônraha. Noien me n…ôha tuho ia narimnari me pam r…ômwhen m…ô kam…ôkwani pen tihinari me ia n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn, Kumwes…ôn s…ô rauvehim…®ru k…®taha.   
\p
\v 11 Krau kraukur…ôn m…ô namasanien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn ruv…ôier pehe raka t…® n…ôrmama me pam. In n…ôha namasanien s…ô rauvehim…®ru n…ôrmama ir…ô.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt 1Jon 2:16, Efes 1:4\x*Namasanien n…ôha ram…ôv…ôha…° m k…®taha m…ô ts…ôni rek…ôm ia noien me s…ôm…ôme Kumwes…ôn ram…ômw…ôki m…®ne noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ôi t…®pr…ôn…ô i n…ôrmama hokeikei p…®k. Ia n…®t…ôt…ô i ipwet m…®ne k…®taha tsam…ôkeikei mhar…ô, mamh…ôukur…ôn nari, mamho noien atukwatukw m…®ne noien me s…ôm…ôme Kumwes…ôn rokeikei,  
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt 1Kor 1:7, Fil 3:20\x*n…ôn…ô, mamh…ôfwini n…ôp…®n amasan n…ôha k…®taha sam…ômri pen …ôknek…®n n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®taha ir…ô. N…ôp…®n amasan n…ôha in n…ô n…ôp…®n s…ô Iesu Kristo trier pehe ir…ô irau n…®skaiien s…ôv…ônhi. Iesu n…ô in Kumwes…ôn asori s…ôk…®taha rauvehim…®ru k…®taha.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Kal 1:4, Eks 19:5, Dut 7:6, Sam 130:8, Esik 37:23, 1Tes 2:9\x*In r…®n…ôseni n…®m…®ruien s…ôv…ônhi memh…ô tukutaha m…ô truvehi raka k…®taha ia noien …ôr…ôha me pam, n…ôn…ô, m…ôp…ôrhi k…®taha s…ômher mh…ôuvehe mho k…®taha n…ôrmama s…ôv…ônhi …ôpa s…ôskai t…® noien amasan me.   
\p
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt 1Tim 4:12\x*Narimnari me i ik tikamahat…ôn n…ôrmama me ir…ô. Tikuvehi ut…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônraha, m…ô…°kiari m…®nraha t…® n…®niseien noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônraha. Ikauvehi nasoriien t…® noien n…ôri i. Pw…ôh i…ôrmama riti r…®pko mh…ô n…ôri au…ôr a ia niram, m…ôpw…ôh mwi n…ôt…ôien t…ôkutam.   
\c 3  
\s1 Noien amasan me s…ôm…ôme Taetas tram…ôkeikei m…ôv…ôha…° m nakalasia me ir…ô  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Rom 13:1-7, 1Tes 2:13-14\x*Taetas. Tiko a pw…ôh rer…®nraha ramrhi m…ô tuh…ôsiai n…ôm…ô asori me m…®ne n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôr…®m…ônu ia nir…ôha. Tuham…ôkeikei mho n…ôkwanraha, n…ôn…ô mh…ôrer mwatuk ia n…ôp…®n me t…® noien amasan me pam.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Fil 4:5\x*Ir…ôha tuh…ôpw…ôh n…®ni …ôr…ôhaien i…ôrmama riti. Ia n…ôp…®n me tuham…ôkeikei mhar…ô ia n…ôm…ôrinuien, mh…ôpw…ôh n…ôvis…ôien, n…ôn…ô mheiwaiu mhasitu ia n…ôrmama me pam.   
\p
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt 1Kor 6:11, Efes 2:2, 5:8\x*Ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mho iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô fwe kupw…ôn k…®taha mwi s…ôreirei nari, mamh…ôrui n…ôkwai Kumwes…ôn. Kameiku…ô ia k…®taha s…ôpw…ôh n…ôt…ôien suatuk atukwatukw. Noien …ôr…ôha me nepw…®n sokeikei p…®k mh…ôre…°i ramasan ir…ô kamh…ôr…®m…ônu ia k…®taha. Ia nar…ôien s…ôk…®taha samo p…®k n…ôr…ôhaien. Rer…®taha ramakres narimnari me s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama. Kam…ômw…ôki k…®taha n…ôn…ô k…®taha sam…ômw…ôki k…®taha me. Fwe kupw…ôn noien s…ôk…®taha ro iam…®nha ir…ô,  
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt Taet 1:3\x*m…ôt…ô Kumwes…ôn s…ô rauvei pehe n…®m…®ruien vi m k…®taha r…ôrhi pehe namasanien m…®ne nokeikeiien s…ôv…ônhi rier pehe tukutaha.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt 2Tim 1:9, Efes 5:26, Jon 3:5\x*Ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha Kumwes…ôn ruvehim…®ru k…®taha. M…ôt…ô in r…®pkuvehim…®ru mh…ô k…®taha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô samo noien amasan me, rek…ôm. In ruvehim…®ru k…®taha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô rapi k…®taha. In ruvehim…®ru k…®taha n…ôp…®n N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan raikuas raka noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôk…®taha, s…ôtui mwi, mh…ôuvehe mh…ôrm…ôvi mwi.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Wok Me 2:17-18\x*Kumwes…ôn r…ôt…ô…°i irapw N…ôn…®mw…®n n…ôha ruvehe muku…ôr ia k…®taha muku pen t…® Iesu Kristo. Iesu n…ôha in i…ôrmama s…ô rauvei pehe n…®m…®ruien vi m k…®taha.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt Rom 3:24\x*In rasitu ia k…®taha ia namasanien s…ôv…ônhi, mo k…®taha satukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn m…ô k…®taha ts…ôuvehi n…®m…®ruien rer…®n s…ô s…ôn…ômri pen …ôknek…®n raka n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®taha ir…ô.  
\v 8 N…ô…°kiariien i in n…ô…°kiariien p…ôrhien. N…ôn…ô iakokeikei m…ô tikahat…ôn amasan n…ôrmama me ia narimnari me i. Pw…ôh n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme h…ôm…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ia Kumwes…ôn tuhamar…ô mamho noien amasan me. Narimnari me i hamasan p…®k mamhasitu ia n…ôrmama.   
\p
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt 2Tim 2:14,16,23\x*M…ôt…ô n…ôresien me n…ôrmama h…ôreirei nari kamh…ôni, m…®ne n…ô…°kiariien me kamh…ôni ia kw…ôn…ôkwus s…ôv…ôi kaha kupw…ôn me, m…®ne n…ôvis…ôien me kamh…ôvis…ô m…®nraha me t…® n…®pwrai Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses, tikam…ôkeikei m…ôrer isipw…®n t…® nir…ôha, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô ko h…ôpkasitu mh…ô, namasanien s…ôv…ônraha riw…ôn.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Mat 18:15-17, 2Jon 10\x*Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô i…ôrmama riti r…®ni n…ô…°kiariien iam…®nhi meitehi k…®miaha ir…ô, tikev…ôn m…®nise. M…ô ro mwi iam…®nhi, n…ôn…ô, tikev…ôn m…®nise mwi. Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô ik…®nise m k…ôru, m…ôt…ô ram…ôkeikei ia noien s…ôv…ônhi, n…ôn…ô, tik…ôrer pen isipw…®n tukwe, m…ôpw…ôh.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt 1Tim 6:3-5\x*Ikukur…ôn m…ô i…ôrmama s…ô ramo iam…®nhi ir…ô, in i…ôm…ô r…ôr…ôha, mamo noien …ôr…ôha. Noien s…ôv…ônhi ramo pui atukw a in m…ô in i…ôrmama riti Kumwes…ôn tr…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ônhi.   
\s1 N…ô…°kiariien sampam s…ôv…ôi Pol  
\p
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt Efes 6:21-22\x*Tak…ôrhi pehe i…ôrman mi i riti Atemas u…ô Tikikas truvehe m…ôtoni ik. N…ôp…®n truvehe ir…ô, tikam…ôkeikei m…ôtoni akwauakw a suatuk m…ô tikuvehe m…ôtoni iou fwe taon n…ôha Nikopolis, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iou iakokeikei m…ô takev…ôn mar…ô fwe ik…®n ia n…ôp…®n s…ôv…ôi n…ôkwieiien.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Wok Me 18:24, 1Kor 3:5-6, 1Kor 16:12\x*I…ôrmama mi k…ôru n…ô…°h…®nrau n…ô Apolos m…®ne Sinas, Sinas in i…ôrmama riti s…ô ramowok ia n…®karen s…ôv…ôi loa s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Rom, irau krauav…ôn ia nav…ônien s…ôv…ônrau, m…ôt…ô tikasitu ia nirau m…ô nari riti tr…ôpw…ôh niw…ôn t…ôniien ia nirau.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Efes 4:28, Taet 2:14, Mat 7:19\x*Ramasan m…ô ikahat…ôn n…ôrmama me s…ôk…®taha m…ô ir…ôha tuhar…ô mamh…ômwur mamho noien amasan me mamhasitu ia n…ôrmama nepw…®n s…ôm…ôme narimnari me s…ôv…ônraha r…®pk…ômwhen mh…ô. R…ôr…ôha m…ô n…ôrmama me s…ôk…®taha tuhamar…ô au…ôr a.   
