\v 15 N…ôrmama me pam s…ôm…ôme kamhar…ô k…®maha m…®nraha h…ôni ramasan tukw ik. N…ôn…ô ik tik…®ni tukwini ramasan s…ôk…®maha rev…ôn t…® n…ôrmama me s…ôm…ôme hokeikei k…®maha mamhahat…ôt…ô ia Iesu.  
